data.description: Move-in Ready! This spacious 3BR/2BA home features: living room w/ vaulted ceiling & beautiful stone surround fireplace, master bedroom w/ private access to rear patio, master bath w/ soaking tub, large walk-in closet & separate shower, spacious secondary bedrooms sharing a hall full bath, kitchen w/ plenty of cabinets, and a dining room w/ additional access door to backyard! Additional features of this remarkable property include a finished bonus room, new carpet, new interior paint, covered front porch, low maintenance vinyl siding, backyard w/ privacy fence, and located close to schools, shopping, I-75, and the McDonough Square. This amazing opportunity awaits your viewing!
